<section class="top-border">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-12">      
		  <h3 class="section-header">What we've been up to</h3>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		
		<div class="col-lg-6">
		  <div class="homepage-highlight">
    


        <p class="lead">Latest article</p>
    <div class="thumbnail-mini">
        <a href="http://www.stellabooks.com/article/john-s-goodall">
                <img src="/images/articles/279/goodall-examples.jpg" alt="John S. Goodall">
                </a>
    </div>
    
    <p class="thumbnail-para"><strong><a href="http://www.stellabooks.com/article/john-s-goodall">John S. Goodall</a></strong><br>
    <small>The ability to tell a story without the use of words was one of the many talents of John S. Goodall. John Strickland Goodall, to give his full name, was born in Heacham in Norfolk&nbsp;in 1908 to Amelia Hunt and Prof. Joseph Strickland Goodall, a famous heart specialist. During his time at Harrow School, and in the years immediately after, he learnt from and worked with such famous artists as Sir Arthur Cope RA, J. Watson Nicol and Harold Speed,...</small>
    </p>

    <p class="thumbnail-para">
        <a href="http://www.stellabooks.com/article/john-s-goodall" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Read more</a>
        <a href="http://www.stellabooks.com/article" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" style="margin: 10px 0"><i class="icon icon-circle-arrow-right" ></i> Browse articles</a>
    </p>


