        <p class="lead">Featured book</p>
    <div class="thumbnail-mini">
        <a href="http://www.stellabooks.com/featured-book/the-forest-ring-by-william-c-de-mille">
                <img src="/images/featured-books/143/forest-ring-1.jpg" alt="The Forest Ring by William C. de Mille">
                </a>
